    <subfield code="o">29</subfield>
    <subfield code="m">It is worth noting that this asymptotic relation is valid in the regime -a2 (µ2 - ω2 ) &lt; m2 [28]. Taking cognizance of (3), one realizes that this inequality is trivially satisfied by the bound-state resonances of the massive scalar fields</subfield>
